  <!--
    en-US (English — source + fallback) string catalogue for the agent (i18n, #323 / part of #320).

    English (en-US) is the source + fallback locale (see <DefaultLanguage> in
    FocusAgent.App.csproj); nl-NL is the Dutch proof-of-concept. Keys must stay
    identical across every locale — I18nCatalogueParityTests locks that. Every
    key is looked up in code via the Loc helper (ResourceLoader over an explicit
    MRT ResourceContext) — the agent ships unpackaged, where the framework's own
    x:Uid resolution can't be pointed at a chosen language.

    DO NOT hand-edit the resheader block below; it is the standard resx schema
    Visual Studio's .resw editor expects.
  -->
